Here follows the singing of the Sanetus, Which is common to all the liturgies. The text of the Mozarabic Missal varies in no respect from that of the Roman text at present in use.

The prayer that follows, Gollectio post Sanctus serves merely to connect the Sanetus with the account of the institution of the Eucharist.
